data.title: ROACH MODE w/ Jon Cross
data.meta_description: Listen to this episode from The Weekly Showcase on Spotify. Wait.... This isn't WCYO?... or is it?. Catch Jon Cross and Alex Royal as they reunite at the Sheezy for the always popular CHRISTMAS EXTRAVAGANZA EPISODE. This is the 5th year in a row Jon & Alex have met and exchanged gifts/stories to bring in Christmas the only way they know how!
